data.text:
Editor's note: The Oklahoman will publish free birth and adoption announcements as space permits. Include full names of parents, sex of child, and hospital or county of adoption. You can mail the information to The Oklahoman, P.O. Box 25125, Oklahoma City, OK 73125.

The Oklahoman has discontinued publishing birth announcements from hospitals that do not provide full names of parents.
